      "form_guide": "",
      "comment": "ROLLING HOME (8) Bivouac two-year-old who made a sound debut with a game on-pace third over 1300m at Warwick Farm. Cross-over nose band goes on for this and looks hard to hold out. FINED FOR SPEEDING (1) much better effort second-up when he attacked the line for an unlucky second over 1280m at this track. Can race a tough closer today and prove hard to stop. FIERCENESS (3) shuffled back early from the inside gate before warming up late with a handy third over 1100m at Mudgee. Finds a winnable race from the good barrier. INCREMENTAL (5) Circus Maximus gelding from a Zabeel mare on debut for the Archibald camp. Has shown enough in the two trials to suggest he can run a forward race.",
